Utterance.UttText: In bed 6, we've got Li Zhou.
He is here for 2 days now.
He came here to visit his granddaughter who just had a baby and it's his first grand child.
During the long flight he felt unwell and the grand daughter said it is difficult to have a normal discussion with him as he doesn't seem to pay attention as he normally does.
He is constantly tachycardic for review.
He walks independently without any assistance.
He can be incontinent at times.
